s=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"content31_component\"><div class=\"content31_content\"><div class=\"text-rich-text w-richtext\"><p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 5, 2025</p><p>QuantFi uses cookies to enhance user experience, analyze website performance, and provide personalized content. This policy explains how we use cookies, the types of cookies we employ, and how users can manage their preferences.</p><p><strong>Legal Basis for Processing Cookies</strong></p><p>For users in the European Economic Area (EEA), the United Kingdom, and other<strong> </strong>jurisdictions with similar regulations, our use of cookies is based on user consent, except for essential cookies, which are necessary for the operation of our Site. By continuing to use our Site, you consent to the use of cookies in accordance with this policy.</p><p><strong>How We Use Cookies</strong></p><p>We use different types of cookies for various purposes:</p><ul role=\"list\"><li><strong>Essential Cookies</strong> \u2013 Required for the core functionality of our Site, including security, authentication, and accessibility. These cookies cannot be disabled.</li><li><strong>Performance Cookies</strong> \u2013 Collect anonymized data on how users interact with the Site to improve usability and performance.</li><li><strong>Advertising Cookies</strong> \u2013 Enable personalized advertising and marketing based on user behavior and preferences.</li><li><strong>Personalization Cookies</strong> \u2013 Tailor content and recommendations to enhance the user experience.</li><li><strong>Third-Party Cookies</strong> \u2013 Set by external providers such as analytics and advertising partners to measure engagement and serve relevant ads. These cookies are governed by their respective third-party privacy policies.</li></ul><p><strong>Consent Mechanism and Managing Cookies</strong></p><p>You can manage or withdraw your consent at any time by adjusting your browser settings. Disabling non-essential cookies may impact the functionality of the Site.</p><p><strong>Third-Party Cookies and External Providers</strong></p><p>Our Site may integrate cookies from third-party providers, including analytics, advertising networks, and social media platforms. These cookies are governed by their respective privacy policies. To learn more, please review the following policies:</p><ul role=\"list\"><li>Google Analytics Privacy Policy</li><li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/policy.php\">Facebook Privacy Policy</a></li></ul><p><strong>Managing Cookies via Browsers and Devices</strong></p><p>You can control and delete cookies through your web browser settings. Below are links to cookie management instructions for major browsers:</p><ul role=\"list\"><li>Google Chrome</li><li><a href=\"https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enable-and-disable-cookies-website-preferences\">Mozilla Firefox</a></li><li><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471/mac\">Apple Safari</a></li><li><a href=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4027947/microsoft-edge-delete-cookies\">Microsoft Edge</a></li></ul><p>For more general information on managing cookies, you can also visit www.allaboutcookies.org.</p><p><strong>Opting Out of Behavioral Advertising</strong></p><p>Users can opt out of interest-based advertising and tracking via industry-standard opt-out mechanisms, such as:</p><ul role=\"list\"><li>Network Advertising Initiative\u2019s Opt-Out Platform</li><li>Digital Advertising Alliance Consumer Choice</li><li><a href=\"https://www.youronlinechoices.eu/\">Your Online Choices (EU Users)</a></li></ul><p><strong>Retention and Expiration of Cookies</strong></p><p>Cookies will automatically expire within 12 months, unless otherwise specified. Some cookies may have shorter retention periods depending on their function, and users may manually delete stored cookies at any time.</p><p><strong>Your Rights and Data Protection</strong></p><p>For California residents under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA/CPRA), certain cookies may be considered as \"sharing\" data for targeted advertising purposes. You have the right to opt out of this sharing through our <strong>\"</strong>Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information\" link [Insert Link].</p><p>For users covered under GDPR, you have the right to access, correct, delete, or restrict the processing of personal data collected via cookies. For further information, please refer to our <a href=\"/legal/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a> or contact us at <a href=\"mailto:cs@quantfi.us\" target=\"_blank\">cs@quantfi.us</a>.</p><p><strong>Policy Updates and Notifications</strong></p><p>QuantFi may update this Cookie Policy periodically to reflect changes in regulations, technology, or our data practices. If significant changes occur, we will notify users through a prominent notice on our Site. We encourage users to review this policy regularly.</p><p>For any questions or concerns regarding our use of cookies, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:cs@quantfi.us\" target=\"_blank\">cs@quantfi.us</a>.</p></div></div><div class=\"content31_newsletter\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6-2\">Follow on Linkedin</div></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><p>Stay connected for regular tips, resources, and practical advice.</p></div><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/quantfi-us/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button w-button\">Follow QuantFi</a></div><div class=\"gradient-blurb is5\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-wf--large-card-section--variant=\"base\" class=\"section_large-card\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div data-animate=\"fade-up\" class=\"layout1_component\" style=\"translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0; transform: translate(0px, 50px);\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid large-card\"><div class=\"large-card_content\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Work With QuantFi</h2></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Connect with us to discuss your goals and explore how our tailored financial support can help.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button is-secondary w-button\">Schedule a Consultation</a></div></div></div><div class=\"large-card_image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-border\"><div class=\"image-inner\"><img data-wf--image--variant=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/68239bb22647b405c2f34fdb_CTA%20Grid.svg\" class=\"image\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"gradient-blurb is2\"></div></div></div></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background.png\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 860px) 100vw, 860px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background.png 860w\" alt=\"\" class=\"grid-bg_right\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background.png\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 860px) 100vw, 860px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background.png 860w\" alt=\"\" class=\"grid-bg_left\" style=\"will-change: opacity; opacity: 0.25;\"></secti